<td>FTI-10020</td>
<td>4027</td>
<td>6/25/2015</td>
<td>7/25/2015</td>
<td>10020</td>
<td>700.00</td>
<td>USD</td>
<td>700.00</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>Discount information appears at the bottom of the <strong>Settle open transactions</strong> page.</p>
<table>
<thead>
