<td>700.00</td>
<td></td>
<td>USD</td>
<td>693.00</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>Discount information appears at the bottom of the <strong>Settle open transactions</strong> page.</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th></th>
<th></th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Cash discount date</td>
<td>7/09/2015</td>
</tr>
